      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i'm typing this. everything just feels so heavy. i spent 5 years on this research and today the lab results basically proved my whole thesis was a dead end. the funding is gone, my advisor won't even look me in the eye, and i just feel... completely empty. like there's nothing left of me. i'm just so tired of fighting. i just want the noise to stop.",
